Business Problem: Identifying high-value customer segments and analyzing retention trends in a wholesale retail environment.

Key Insights Found:

Retention: The Dec-2010 cohort showed a 35% retention rate by Month 3, significantly higher than subsequent cohorts.

Geography: 82% of revenue is driven by UK-registered customers; however, Germany has a 15% higher Average Order Value (AOV).

Segments: Identified 12% of the customer base as "Champions" using RFM scoring.

Tech Stack: Pandas, NumPy
